        "subject": "LU-20004 build: add support for Ubuntu 24.04.3 kernel 6.8.0-106",
        "message": "LU-20004 build: add support for Ubuntu 24.04.3 kernel 6.8.0-106\n\nAdd ldiskfs patches and build configuration for Ubuntu 24.04.3\nkernel version 6.8.0-106.\n\n- Add ext4-delayed-iput.patch for Ubuntu 24.04.3\n- Add ext4-pdirop.patch for Ubuntu 24.04.3\n- Add ldiskfs-6.8.0-106-ubuntu24.series patch series\n- Update lustre-build-ldiskfs.m4 to select 6.8.0-106 series for\n  kernel patch level >= 106\n- Update default fallback series to 6.8.0-106\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nChange-Id: I2a99d6c08dc6b2bffebfa4359168e8f18115ca69\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64617\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
